  m_Name: HighAfNarration 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - I walk out into an alleyway after getting lunch and coffee.
  - A strange feeling pulls me towrds it.
  - I check my surroundings, making sure nobody is watching me.
  - The further I walk, the further the alley seems to stretch.
  - A chill runs up my spine as I turn around.
  - Nothing is there.
  - I could've sworn I felt-
